               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17831210-13-cd84" type="crimeDate">24th day of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17831210-13-off83 t17831210-13-cd84"></join> last, four pair of mens leather shoes value 14 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17831210-13-victim248" type="victimName">
